Expense Tracker
Features
1. Authentication
•	Register user 
•	Login user 
•	Logout user
2. User Management
•	Get profile 
•	Update profile 
•	Delete account
3. Expenses
•	Add expense 
•	Get all expenses 
•	Get single expense 
•	Update expense 
•	Delete expense
4. Income
•	Add income 
•	Get all income 
•	Get single income 
•	Update income 
•	Delete income
5. Categories
•	Create category 
•	Get categories 
•	Update category 
•	Delete category
6. Dashboard
•	Total income 
•	Total expenses 
•	Balance 
•	Recent transactions
7. Reports
•	Monthly expense report 
•	Category breakdown 
•	Yearly summary
8. Security
•	JWT authentication 
•	Password hashing 
•	User data protection (each user sees only their data)
9. Filtering (VERY important)
Allow users to search and narrow results.
Expenses / Income filters:
•	by date range (from – to) 
•	by category 
•	by type (income or expense if combined model)
10. Pagination
So data doesn’t load all at once.
What it does:
•	returns data in pages instead of everything

